Dontrey Lynch WEBSTER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0736 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. March 27, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petitioner's motion for State of Florida to concede illegal sentence is denied as an unauthorized filing in this court.
